{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idef18a7c3-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1982"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1982"},"text":"§ 1982.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Relief for mobilized military reservists from certain agricultural loan obligations","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idef18a7c4-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1982/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Definition of mobilized military reservist","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"In this section, the term “mobilized military reservist” means an individual who—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idef18a7c5-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1982/a/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" is on active duty under section 688, 12301(a), 12301(g), 12302, 12304, 12306, or 12406, or chapter 13 of title 10, or any other provision of law during a war or during a national emergency declared by the President or Congress, regardless of the location at which the active duty service is performed; or","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idef18a7c6-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1982/a/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" in the case of a member of the National Guard, is on full-time National Guard duty (as defined in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s101/d/5"},"text":"section 101(d)(5) of title 10","children":[],"tail":") under a call to active service authorized by the President or the Secretary of Defense for a period of more than 30 consecutive days under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t32/s502/f"},"text":"section 502(f) of title 32","children":[],"tail":" for purposes of responding to a national emergency declared by the President and supported by Federal funds."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idef18a7c7-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1982/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Forgiveness of interest payments due while borrower is a mobilized military reservist","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Any requirement that a borrower of a direct loan made under this chapter make any interest payment on the loan that would otherwise be required to be made while the borrower is a mobilized military reservist is rescinded.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idef18a7c8-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1982/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Deferral of principal payments due while or after borrower is a mobilized military reservist","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The due date of any payment of principal on a direct loan made to a borrower under this chapter that would otherwise be required to be made while or after the borrower is a mobilized military reservist is deferred for a period equal in length to the period for which the borrower is a mobilized military reservist.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idef18a7c9-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1982/d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"d"},"text":"(d)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Nonaccrual of interest","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Interest on a direct loan made to a borrower described in this section shall not accrue during the period the borrower is a mobilized military reservist.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idef18a7ca-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1982/e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"e"},"text":"(e)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Borrower not considered to be delinquent or receiving debt forgiveness","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Notwithstanding ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s2008h"},"text":"section 2008h of this title","children":[],"tail":" or any other provision of this chapter, a borrower who receives assistance under this section shall not, as a result of the assistance, be considered to be delinquent or receiving debt forgiveness for purposes of receiving a direct or guaranteed loan under this chapter."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idef18a7cb-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/87/128/tIII/s332"},"text":"Pub. L. 87–128, title III, § 332","children":[],"tail":", as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/108/375/dA/tVI/s664"},"text":"Pub. L. 108–375, div. A, title VI, § 664","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2004-10-28"},"text":"Oct. 28, 2004","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/118/1974"},"text":"118 Stat. 1974","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/232/dA/tXII/s1204/a/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–232, div. A, title XII, § 1204(a)(2)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2018-08-13"},"text":"Aug. 13, 2018","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/132/2017"},"text":"132 Stat. 2017","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idef18a7cc-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idef18a7cd-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idef18a7ce-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"This chapter, referred to in subsecs. (b), (c), and (e), was in the original “this title”, meaning title III of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/87/128"},"text":"Pub. L. 87–128","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1961-08-08"},"text":"Aug. 8, 1961","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/75/307"},"text":"75 Stat. 307","children":[],"tail":", known as the Consolidated Farm and Rural Development Act. For complete classification of title III to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s1921"},"text":"section 1921 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"priorProvisions","id":"idef18a7cf-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Prior Provisions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"A prior section 1982, ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/87/128/tIII/s332"},"text":"Pub. L. 87–128, title III, § 332","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1961-08-08"},"text":"Aug. 8, 1961","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/75/314"},"text":"75 Stat. 314","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/198/tXIII/s1311"},"text":"Pub. L. 99–198, title XIII, § 1311","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1985-12-23"},"text":"Dec. 23, 1985","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/99/1524"},"text":"99 Stat. 1524","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/233/tVI/s607"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–233, title VI, § 607","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1988-01-06"},"text":"Jan. 6, 1988","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/101/1667"},"text":"101 Stat. 1667","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/624/tXVIII/s1809"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–624, title XVIII, § 1809","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1990-11-28"},"text":"Nov. 28, 1990","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/104/3820"},"text":"104 Stat. 3820","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/554/s11"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–554, § 11","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-10-28"},"text":"Oct. 28, 1992","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/106/4151"},"text":"106 Stat. 4151","children":[],"tail":", related to county committees, prior to repeal by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/354/tII/s227/b/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–354, title II, § 227(b)(1)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1994-10-13"},"text":"Oct. 13, 1994","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/108/3218"},"text":"108 Stat. 3218","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"idef18a7d0-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2018—Subsec. (a)(1). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/232"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–232","children":[],"tail":" substituted “chapter 13” for “chapter 15”."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
